data.description:
You are in LUCK! Take advantage of the dramatic price reduction before it is gone, gone, gone.  This stunning desert oasis home has been lived in by one owner who brought their imagination and charm to this solid, semi-custom brick home. Imagine waking up to the sound of birdsong and the smell of the desert air. Step outside onto your private patio and take in the breathtaking views of the Catalina Mountains. The towering saguaro cacti and Eucalyptus and Pine trees provide a sense of peace and tranquility, while the starry nights and glorious sunsets are simply magical. Relax in your hammock and soak up the sunshine. This beautifully crafted brick home is spacious and comfortable, with plenty of room for family and friends. The kitchen is fully equipped, and the sunken living room is perfect for entertaining. There are 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Discover the potential hidden within this charming home and a layout that promises versatility. This home is located just minutes from the city, but it feels like a world away. With almost an acre of property and no HOA, this is  the perfect place to find peace and quiet, while still being close to all the amenities you need. Enjoy hiking, biking, and horseback riding in the surrounding mountains. 

Call today to schedule a showing!
